                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "1fe547cf4fa111c9e8976c3476d9c9d7",
                "text": "The armor covers you so completely that it provides benefits against some damaging effects. On Reflex saves to avoid a damaging effect, such as a fireball, you add a +3 modifier instead of your Dexterity modifier",
                "classes": [
                    "trait"
                ]
