                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "4f1ffc523f6984a9aa1d59f318785908",
                "text": "The armor is made up of layered sections, so when it breaks, it isn't as much of a problem. The status penalty to AC if this armor is broken is \u20131 for broken medium armor, \u20132 for broken heavy armor, or no penalty for broken light armor.",
